      <title>英国商业偏好调查中工党大幅领先</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-01/labour-scores-large-lead-in-survey-of-uk-business-preference</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一项针对英国公司领导人的民意调查显示，工党是对企业最有利的政党，这表明反对党争取企业界支持的努力正在取得成效。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-01/labour-scores-large-lead-in-survey-of-uk-business-preference</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 01 Jun 2024 15:56:58 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
