    <item>
      <title>祖马夺回非洲人国民大会对南非夸祖鲁-纳塔尔省的控制权</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-01/zuma-sweeps-anc-from-control-of-south-africa-s-kwazulu-natal</link>
      <description><![CDATA[非洲人国民大会在南非人口第二多的夸祖​​鲁-纳塔尔省失利，选民坚决拒绝该党，转而支持前总统雅各布·祖马领导的政党。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-01/zuma-sweeps-anc-from-control-of-south-africa-s-kwazulu-natal</guid>
