    <item>
      <title>对于 Sheinbaum 来说，罗塞夫的崛起和衰落是一个警示故事</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-01/for-claudia-sheinbaum-rise-and-fall-of-dilma-rousseff-is-a-cautionary-tale</link>
      <description><![CDATA[想象一下：一位非常受欢迎的总统无法竞选连任，他希望通过任命一位更具技术官僚气质的女性继任者来巩固自己的政治遗产，成为该国首位女总统。这概括了墨西哥克劳迪娅·辛鲍姆的崛起。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-01/for-claudia-sheinbaum-rise-and-fall-of-dilma-rousseff-is-a-cautionary-tale</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 01 Jun 2024 12:30:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>奥尔班在欧盟投票前举行大型集会以展示力量</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-01/eu-election-orban-holds-major-rally-in-budapest-in-show-of-force</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在匈牙利地方选举和欧盟选举即将到来、强大竞争对手即将出现之际，数万名匈牙利总理维克托·奥尔班的支持者聚集在布达佩斯，为这位民族主义领袖展示力量。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-01/eu-election-orban-holds-major-rally-in-budapest-in-show-of-force</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 01 Jun 2024 11:58:51 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
