    <item>
      <title>南非非国大在得票率达到 99% 的情况下权力崩溃</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-01/south-african-election-a-historic-rebuke-for-the-anc</link>
      <description><![CDATA[南非执政党非洲人国民大会即将首次放弃议会多数席位，因为选民对纳尔逊·曼德拉在种族隔离制度结束时领导的政党进行了历史性的谴责。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-01/south-african-election-a-historic-rebuke-for-the-anc</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 01 Jun 2024 06:47:12 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>印度漫长选举结束，莫迪第三任期前景不明朗</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-01/india-s-long-bitter-election-fight-heads-toward-finish-line</link>
      <description><![CDATA[经过六个多星期的投票，印度马拉松式的大选于周六落下帷幕，人们的焦点目前转向出口民调，该结果让人们首次看到总理纳伦德拉·莫迪是否能够延续其十年的执政。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-01/india-s-long-bitter-election-fight-heads-toward-finish-line</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 01 Jun 2024 04:26:39 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国称新的加沙停火提议是“决定性时刻”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-31/biden-raises-pressure-on-israel-hamas-for-deal-to-end-war</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国表示，新的停火提议将使以色列和哈马斯之间的战斗暂停至少六周，这可能标志着冲突的“决定性时刻”——如果双方在几次和平尝试失败后达成一致。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-31/biden-raises-pressure-on-israel-hamas-for-deal-to-end-war</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 31 May 2024 18:22:44 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
